\f[C]result\f[R] \- a result set identifier returned by
\f[B]mysql_store_result(3)\f[R] or \f[B]mysql_use_result(3)\f[R].
.SS Notes
.IP \[bu] 2
The field order will be reset if you execute a new SELECT query.
.IP \[bu] 2
