be selected by using the \f[B]mysql_field_seek(3)\f[R] function or
obtained by \f[B]mysql_fetch_field_direct(3)\f[R] function.
.SS Return value
.PP
a pointer of a \f[C]MYSQL_FIELD\f[R] structure, or NULL if there are no
more fields.
